", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1650095309", "stars": 4372, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 204076, "username": "supermao", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/supermao", "website": "https://fengxiaomao.com", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "hongmaoxiao", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "三十立不了，四十解不了惑，五十活到那时再说吧", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/db33/f16f/204076_mini.png?m=1654076396", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/db33/f16f/204076_normal.png?m=1654076396", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/db33/f16f/204076_large.png?m=1654076396", "created": 1480656130, "last_modified": 1654076396}, "last_reply_by": "takato", "last_touched": 1654153257, "title": "上海解封了，而我写的小程序更像是 49 年入股国军", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/856782", "created": 1654076968, "deleted": 0, "content": "这是一个可以记录自己在疫情期间每一天的核酸、抗原以及被封控的情况的微信小程序。\r\n\r\n小程序名字是: 核日历\r\n\r\n传送门:\r\n![qrcode]( https://file.fengxiaomao.com/omicron/root.png)\r\n\r\n以下是一个保存结果图片的样例:\r\n![qrcode]( https://file.fengxiaomao.com/omicron/11111.JPG)\r\n\r\n\r\n既然熬了 2 3 个通宵出来的东西，我就试着分享下，看看有没有人会用吧", "content_rendered": "<p>这是一个可以记录自己在疫情期间每一天的核酸、抗原以及被封控的情况的微信小程序。</p>\n<p>小程序名字是: 核日历</p>\n<p>传送门:\n<img alt=\"qrcode\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://file.fengxiaomao.com/omicron/root.png\"/></p>\n<p>以下是一个保存结果图片的样例:\n<img alt=\"qrcode\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://file.fengxiaomao.com/omicron/11111.JPG\"/></p>\n<p>既然熬了 2 3 个通宵出来的东西，我就试着分享下，看看有没有人会用吧</p>\n", "last_modified": 1654076968, "replies": 88, "id": 856782}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 185511, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3488, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 534563, "username": "ACVV", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ACVV", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/498cd228f845996ed68e5e77299c68e7?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/498cd228f845996ed68e5e77299c68e7?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/498cd228f845996ed68e5e77299c68e7?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1614149170, "last_modified": 1631257546}, "last_reply_by": "Cagliostro", "last_touched": 1654153596, "title": "几年不看小说了，最近动漫剧荒，求近几年出的好看小说，文笔好点的武侠、玄幻类，最好完本的，拒绝小白文。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/856776", "created": 1654076041, "deleted": 0, "content": "比如，英雄志。可惜最后几章孙狗不更了。除了每次开章铺垫太多，啰嗦不知所云，感觉还算一部佳作啊", "content_rendered": "比如，英雄志。可惜最后几章孙狗不更了。除了每次开章铺垫太多，啰嗦不知所云，感觉还算一部佳作啊", "last_modified": 1654076184, "replies": 87, "id": 856776}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_large.png?m=1614702882", "name": "nas", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_normal.png?m=1614702882", "title": "NAS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas", "topics": 620, "footer": "", "header": "关于网络存储设备的讨论", "title_alternative": "NAS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1614702882", "stars": 1005, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 949, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 61690, "username": "ferock", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ferock", "website": "", "twitter": "JonahFu", "psn": "", "github": "ferocknew", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b903/95f9/61690_mini.png?m=1398964984", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b903/95f9/61690_normal.png?m=1398964984", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b903/95f9/61690_large.png?m=1398964984", "created": 1398964947, "last_modified": 1398964984}, "last_reply_by": "vmos", "last_touched": 1654153027, "title": "观 nas 贴有感", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/856836", "created": 1654106632, "deleted": 0, "content": "原帖地址： https://www.v2ex.com/t/856704?p=1<br>我的回复在#49 ，内容如下：<br><br>很多人搞错了，nas 不是个人 server ，nas 只是存储。<br>你没有存储量级的需求，当然是并不刚性需求 nas<br>综上，你只是需要一个 mini 个人 server 罢了<br><br>但是一想，这并不是用户的问题，其实现在卖家误导了太多。<br>单盘（无数据冗余安全）也叫 nas ，插个 usb 的也叫 nas…<br>jd 搜 nas 关键词，各种妖魔鬼怪夹杂在搜索结果中。<br><br>我随便举例，￼￼联想个人云 A1 nas ，￼￼ ￼￼大迈（ DM ）网络存储器 nas AirDisk Q2 个人网盘，￼￼贝锐蒲公英 蒲公英 X1 路由器旁路组网盒子自建私有云硬盘变云盘网络存储异地组网 DIY 家用 Nas X1￼￼，￼￼雷克沙时光机个人云盘 M1 网络存储器 nas 个人家庭云……<br><br>这些也好意思叫 NAS （ Network Attached Storage ）<br>数据安全，数据容量，数据性能，稳定，个人用户再在意那么点体积、噪音和功耗。<br><br>现在和数据无关的都可以这么厚脸皮了？", "content_rendered": "<p>原帖地址： <a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/856704?p=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.v2ex.com/t/856704?p=1</a><br/>我的回复在#49 ，内容如下：<br/><br/>很多人搞错了，nas 不是个人 server ，nas 只是存储。<br/>你没有存储量级的需求，当然是并不刚性需求 nas<br/>综上，你只是需要一个 mini 个人 server 罢了<br/><br/>但是一想，这并不是用户的问题，其实现在卖家误导了太多。<br/>单盘（无数据冗余安全）也叫 nas ，插个 usb 的也叫 nas…<br/>jd 搜 nas 关键词，各种妖魔鬼怪夹杂在搜索结果中。<br/><br/>我随便举例，￼￼联想个人云 A1 nas ，￼￼ ￼￼大迈（ DM ）网络存储器 nas AirDisk Q2 个人网盘，￼￼贝锐蒲公英 蒲公英 X1 路由器旁路组网盒子自建私有云硬盘变云盘网络存储异地组网 DIY 家用 Nas X1￼￼，￼￼雷克沙时光机个人云盘 M1 网络存储器 nas 个人家庭云……<br/><br/>这些也好意思叫 NAS （ Network Attached Storage ）<br/>数据安全，数据容量，数据性能，稳定，个人用户再在意那么点体积、噪音和功耗。<br/><br/>现在和数据无关的都可以这么厚脸皮了？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1654106632, "replies": 57, "id": 856836}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1651385949", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1651385949", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 49062, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1651385949", "stars": 7844, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 366406, "username": "opentrade", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/opentrade", "website": "https://rustdesk.com", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "SG", "tagline": "主人何为言少钱，径须沽取对君酌", "bio": "https://github.com/rustdesk/rustdesk", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3bde/bf6c/366406_mini.png?m=1543388759", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3bde/bf6c/366406_normal.png?m=1543388759", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3bde/bf6c/366406_large.png?m=1543388759", "created": 1543387714, "last_modified": 1543388759}, "last_reply_by": "superhxl", "last_touched": 1654148140, "title": "是不是只有老司机才记得 Thunderbird？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/856850", "created": 1654131432, "deleted": 0, "content": "其实我也不大记得，很多年前用过一段时间，还有 Foxmail ，那时候 MSN 还流行，ICQ 还活跃，今日同框，恍若隔世。\r\nhttps://twitter.com/mozthunderbird/status/1531938824900714496", "content_rendered": "<p>其实我也不大记得，很多年前用过一段时间，还有 Foxmail ，那时候 MSN 还流行，ICQ 还活跃，今日同框，恍若隔世。\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mozthunderbird/status/1531938824900714496\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://twitter.com/mozthunderbird/status/1531938824900714496</a></p>\n", "last_modified": 1654131432, "replies": 56, "id": 856850}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1651385949", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1651385949", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 49062, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1651385949", "stars": 7844, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 206370, "username": "waiaan", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/waiaan", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a703/deb0/206370_mini.png?m=1651022707", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a703/deb0/206370_normal.png?m=1651022707", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a703/deb0/206370_large.png?m=1651022707", "created": 1481893530, "last_modified": 1651022707}, "last_reply_by": "ybnsjl", "last_touched": 1654149298, "title": "有没有什么设备或者方法可以代替纸和笔用来打草稿的？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/856739", "created": 1654069597, "deleted": 0, "content": "看书或者写代码的时候要打草稿、画画图什么的，这些草稿过后就没用了。想找一个可以重复利用的东西，不然实在是费纸和笔。\r\n目前想到的是手写板，其它还有什么好办法没？\r\n谢谢。", "content_rendered": "<p>看书或者写代码的时候要打草稿、画画图什么的，这些草稿过后就没用了。想找一个可以重复利用的东西，不然实在是费纸和笔。\n目前想到的是手写板，其它还有什么好办法没？\n谢谢。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1654069597, "replies": 56, "id": 856739}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 185511, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3488, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 187904, "username": "dayeye2006199", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/dayeye2006199", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c94dd32e4893e6adede68c44aee77ac0?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c94dd32e4893e6adede68c44aee77ac0?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c94dd32e4893e6adede68c44aee77ac0?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1471630236, "last_modified": 1650392706}, "last_reply_by": "hodlbit", "last_touched": 1654152052, "title": "人在美国，需要向国内交付 10G 左右的文件，有什么比较快速稳定的解决方案", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/856842", "created": 1654127369, "deleted": 0, "content": "10G 主要都是一些二进制，docker 私有镜像之类的文件，文件比较大，都是几百 M\r\n\r\n这些文件有多个客户都需要下载，一个月流量大概有个 1 到 2 个 T 把。\r\n\r\n怎么交付比较快捷、稳定和经济呢？现在想到的几个办法：\r\n1. 亚洲区的 AWS S3\r\n2. 其他类 S3 服务，例如 blackblaze 等\r\n3. S3 + CDN\r\n4. 没有被墙的网盘服务例如 onedrive\r\n\r\n（没有国内的手机号，所以没法注册国内的各种网盘服务）", "content_rendered": "10G 主要都是一些二进制，docker 私有镜像之类的文件，文件比较大，都是几百 M<br /><br />这些文件有多个客户都需要下载，一个月流量大概有个 1 到 2 个 T 把。<br /><br />怎么交付比较快捷、稳定和经济呢？现在想到的几个办法：<br />1. 亚洲区的 AWS S3<br />2. 其他类 S3 服务，例如 blackblaze 等<br />3. S3 + CDN<br />4. 没有被墙的网盘服务例如 onedrive<br /><br />（没有国内的手机号，所以没法注册国内的各种网盘服务）", "last_modified": 1654127369, "replies": 48, "id": 856842}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_large.png?m=1630643933", "name": "mbp", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_normal.png?m=1630643933", "title": "MacBook Pro", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp", "topics": 8027, "footer": "", "header": "State-of-the-art processors. All-new graphics. Breakthrough high-speed I/O. Three very big leaps forward.", "title_alternative": "MacBook Pro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1630643933", "stars": 3108, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 10, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 36154, "username": "fivesmallq", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/fivesmallq", "website": "https://nll.im", "twitter": "fivesmallq", "psn": "", "github": "fivesmallq", "btc": "", "location": "北京", "tagline": "时间终能带来结果，无论正负。", "bio": "时间终能带来结果，无论正负。", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9451/def5/36154_mini.png?m=1654130881", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9451/def5/36154_normal.png?m=1654130881", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9451/def5/36154_large.png?m=1654130881", "created": 1363683242, "last_modified": 1654130881}, "last_reply_by": "hun2008hun", "last_touched": 1654153304, "title": "MacBook Pro 显示器选择", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/856849", "created": 1654130926, "deleted": 0, "content": "MacBook Pro (15-inch, 2019) 准备配置个显示器，昨天到货了 DELL U2723QX 27 寸，反向 90w 充电挺方便的，但是发现颜色偏的好严重，调了半天和 mac 自己的屏幕还是差很多，分辨率有点不适应，用的 2304 * 1296 凑合了。问下各位朋友有什么好的办法吗？\r\n\r\n另外就是要不要换 LG UltraFine 4K ，目前京东和官网都有货，哪个渠道购买会更好一些呢？\r\n\r\n* 官网 可分 24 期，苹果会不会稍微兜底下？听说 LG UltraFine 像是抽奖\r\n* 京东 可以购买一些其他额外保修服务，但是是三方提供的，不知道效果如何，如图\r\n\r\nhttps://imgur.com/a/PyeT42R\r\n\r\n![京东服务]( https://i.imgur.com/xwYyv3m.jpeg)", "content_rendered": "<p>MacBook Pro (15-inch, 2019) 准备配置个显示器，昨天到货了 DELL U2723QX 27 寸，反向 90w 充电挺方便的，但是发现颜色偏的好严重，调了半天和 mac 自己的屏幕还是差很多，分辨率有点不适应，用的 2304 * 1296 凑合了。问下各位朋友有什么好的办法吗？</p>\n<p>另外就是要不要换 LG UltraFine 4K ，目前京东和官网都有货，哪个渠道购买会更好一些呢？</p>\n<ul>\n<li>官网 可分 24 期，苹果会不会稍微兜底下？听说 LG UltraFine 像是抽奖</li>\n<li>京东 可以购买一些其他额外保修服务，但是是三方提供的，不知道效果如何，如图</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgur.com/a/PyeT42R\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://imgur.com/a/PyeT42R</a></p>\n<p><img alt=\"京东服务\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xwYyv3m.jpeg\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1654131213, "replies": 48, "id": 856849}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a5bf/c9e0/37_large.png?m=1584385790", "name": "kindle", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a5bf/c9e0/37_normal.png?m=1584385790", "title": "Kindle", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/kindle", "topics": 441, "footer": "", "header": "Amazon 公司设计生产的电子阅读设备", "title_alternative": "Kindle", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a5bf/c9e0/37_mini.png?m=1584385790", "stars": 1157, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 37, "parent_node_name": "reading"}, "member": {"id": 82783, "username": "hhylx1950", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hhylx1950", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a38fa2ebe3c4b3a07dcbf516b0d7e679?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a38fa2ebe3c4b3a07dcbf516b0d7e679?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a38fa2ebe3c4b3a07dcbf516b0d7e679?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1416502085, "last_modified": 1416502085}, "last_reply_by": "Trim21", "last_touched": 1654153620, "title": "Kindle 将在中国停止电子书店的运营", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/856939", "created": 1654150662, "deleted": 0, "content": "见 https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/jJG36Hbrw2-ZeUT3aDXKBA\r\n> 亚马逊将于一年之后即 2023 年 6 月 30 日，在中国停止 Kindle 电子书店的运营。在此之后，您将不能购买新的电子书。对于已经购买的电子书，您可以在 2024 年 6 月 30 日之前下载，并且可以在此后继续阅读。", "content_rendered": "<p>见 <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/jJG36Hbrw2-ZeUT3aDXKBA\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/jJG36Hbrw2-ZeUT3aDXKBA</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>亚马逊将于一年之后即 2023 年 6 月 30 日，在中国停止 Kindle 电子书店的运营。在此之后，您将不能购买新的电子书。对于已经购买的电子书，您可以在 2024 年 6 月 30 日之前下载，并且可以在此后继续阅读。</p>\n</blockquote>\n", "last_modified": 1654150662, "replies": 38, "id": 856939}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 185511, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3488, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 560585, "username": "Features", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Features", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0616/67df/560585_mini.png?m=1653974242", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0616/67df/560585_normal.png?m=16539742